{
  "chapter": 17,
  "chapter_summary": "马如龙在杂货店照看醒来的谢玉宝，继续以张荣发、王桂枝夫妻身份安抚她。谢玉宝拒绝相信，暴露出自称神的女儿的狂傲和被困后的恐惧，马如龙却守住不乘人之危的底线。平凡日子使他开始反省旧日骄矜，但一个每日黄昏来买大量鸡蛋、草纸、粗盐、米酒的高瘦男人打破平静。马如龙从对方手脚、步法、耐寒等细节判断其是武林好手。姓于的小媳妇追查到他进入陶保义家，又因探问买盐用途被陶保义借故吵架挡开。张老实赶走小媳妇并厌恶闲事，使马如龙首次觉得这个老实人也不简单。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你再说一遍。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "说你是什么人？我是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我是张荣发，你是王桂枝。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我们是夫妻？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "是十八年的夫妻。我们一直都住在这里，开了这家杂货店，附近的每个人都认得我们。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "也许你认为我们这种日子过得太贫苦，已经不想再过了，所以要把以前的事全部都忘记。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "其实，这种日子也没有什么不好，至少，我们一直过得心安理得。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你听着，",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我不知道你是什么人，也不知道这是怎么回事，可是我知道这些事一定是别人买通了你，来害我的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "谁要害你！为什么要害你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你真的不知道我是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "你自己以为你是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "如果你知道我是什么人，说不定会活活骇死。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我是神的女儿，世上没有一个女人能比得上我，我随时都可以让你发财，也随时可以杀了你，所以你最好赶快把我送回去，否则我迟早有一天，要把你一刀刀的割碎，拿去喂狗。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "你的病又犯了，还是早点睡吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你敢睡上来，敢碰我一下，我就……我就……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yu_de_xiao_xi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "姓于的小媳妇",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这个人是谁？我怎么从来没有见过他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yu_de_xiao_xi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "姓于的小媳妇",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这个男人绝不是住在这里的，而且以前绝对没有到这里来过。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你们说的这个人，真的是个男人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "当然是个男人。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他会不会是女扮男装的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "绝不会。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "你为什么要问这件事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "难道你希望他是个女人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "如果他是女人，就可能是来救我的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "你嫁给我十八年，我对你一向不错，别人为什么要来救你？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yu_de_xiao_xi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "姓于的小媳妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道了，我知道了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yu_de_xiao_xi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "姓于的小媳妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道那个人住在哪里了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_xing_yu_de_xiao_xi_fu",
      "text": "他住在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yu_de_xiao_xi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "姓于的小媳妇",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "就住在陶保义的家，",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yu_de_xiao_xi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "姓于的小媳妇",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "我亲眼看见他进去的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yu_de_xiao_xi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "姓于的小媳妇",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "刚才我故意到保义嫂家里去串门子，前前后后都看不见那个人，可是我明明看见那个人到他家去了，我偷偷的问保义嫂，那个人每天买两斤盐回去干什么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yu_de_xiao_xi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "姓于的小媳妇",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "保义哥忽然就借了个原因，跟保义嫂吵起架来，我只有赶紧开溜。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_xing_yu_de_xiao_xi_fu",
      "text": "今天你买不买红糖？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yu_de_xiao_xi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "姓于的小媳妇",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "今天不买。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_xing_yu_de_xiao_xi_fu",
      "text": "买不买酱菜？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_yu_de_xiao_xi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "姓于的小媳妇",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "也不买。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_xing_yu_de_xiao_xi_fu",
      "text": "那么你为什么还不回去睡觉？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "管人闲事最不好，喜欢管闲事的人，我看见就讨厌。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 225
    }
  ],
